Subscriptions, Free Trials, Promotion Subscriptions, Billing and Cancellation

Billing
By starting your subscription and providing or designating a Payment Method, you authorize us to charge you a recurring subscription fee at the then current rate, and any other charges you may incur in connection with your use of our Service to your Payment Method.
